from the meteorological information , we knew the results caused by el nino phenomena last year , including continual violent fire in indonesia , the deluge-flooded desert in peru , and serious abnormal climate in wide areas all around the world .
in america , at the beginning of this year , the flood attacked california and many states in southern area , and then drought hit many places in southern parts .
according to meteorological specialists , the el nino is changing into another new phenomenon called la nina .
and next year , la nina will have a frightening behavior at least as strong as el nino .
now , please listen to a report of voa correspondent li lan from chicago and read by qi zhifen .
last winter , it was much warmer than those usually freezing winters in chicago and with less snow , and it could be very similar next winter .
at the same time , el nino swept fiercely in southeast asia , the rainfall greatly reduced and the drought resulted in a prairie fire burning for several weeks out of control .
both el nino and la nina are the result of a considerable temperature change in surface water in east pacific ocean in the tropics .
el nino means the temperature of surface water in the ocean is much higher than usual , it will affect air current situation , and in turn it will change the climate in different regions in the world .
while la nina means the temperature of surface water in the ocean is much lower than usual , and its influence on many regional climate is just contrary to el nino .
the climate specialist , lavo , of u.s. national bureau of meteorology said that the big fire in indonesia next year wouldn &apos;t be out of control because it was estimated that the rainfall in this area from december this year to march next year would be more than that in past years .
meanwhile , the temperature in west and southeast africa will be a little lower than normal time , and rainfall in northern part of south america will be more .
the southern part of america will be drier than usual . it means there could be a lasting drought in texas and new mexico , and the possibility of big forest fire in florida will be higher than normal .
all the rainstorms in california and southern region this year were imputed to el nino .
lavo said that the el nino won &apos;t produce rainstorm itself , but it will offer conditions of forming the serious rainstorm .
this summer is one of the hottest summers in u.s.
somebody connect global warming to el nino phenomena .
lavo thinks it is possible , but has not been confirmed so far .
but whatever the other reason is , it means the coming winter in north and middle west part of u.s. will be a much colder winter , a winter with more snow .
