dinosaur bone fossil found in henan xixia
xinhua news agency , zhengzhou , april 23 ( by journalist liu yamin ) - recently , some interested specialists and scholars have found plenty of dinosaur bone fossil in yancheng town , xixia county of henan province .
this was another significant discovery followed the findings of rich precious dinosaur egg fossils in this same place last year .
the journalist knew from the cultural relic archaeology research institute of henan province , at the beginning of april this year , the relevant specialists found several hundred pieces of dinosaur bone fossils , some were rib and phalange etc , between two river gravel layers in places of hutoushan mountain , yancheng town of xixia county .
because of their long time exposure on the ground surface , some of them were broken .
from the stratigraphy point of view , all of them belong to the cretaceous period .
according to specialist &apos;s judgment , there could be a great number of dinosaur bone fossils and fossils of other species in this dinosaur fossil concentrated area .
they thought , if the finding of plenty precious dinosaur egg fossils in xixia basin is a rare case in the world , the discovery of both egg fossils and bone fossils in the same place will be much more scarce .
this has a very important significance for studies of classification of dinosaur in xixia area , probe of the dinosaur ecological habit and propagation behavior , restoration of ecological environment of dinosaur times , revelation of the rules of the earth &apos;s crust transition and earth environment evolution etc .
and the finding of dinosaur bone fossils will provide important clues for searching the geographical location and burying rules of the dinosaur fossils .
