heavy rain in guilin brings all pleasure-boats on lijiang to anchor
guilin , june.16 ( xinhua , cheng tianhu ) -in order to ensure the safety of domestic and foreign tourists , relevant departments of guilin municipality today cancelled all shipping activities on lijiang river , the &quot; golden waterway &quot; for travelers , due to heavy rain in guilin from june 14 to 16 .
