in guilin water transport management center , our correspondent saw a few agency groups and individual tourists returning lijiang pleasant-boat tickets in an orderly way .
&quot; for the sake of tourist safety , we stopped all pleasant-boat trips today , &quot; said pan changli , deputy director of the center .
