eu to take retaliatory measures against us in steel trade dispute
brussel , june.18 ( xinhua , tian fan ) -eu might take retaliatory measures against us in steel trade dispute , the eu commission announced on 18th , and they have formally notify the world trade organization of this .
after the eu commission had circulated a formal notice to wto , &quot; eu would go ahead with the retaliatory tariff on us goods . &quot; said gooch , spokesman of the eu commission on a press conference .
he added that eu would make the final punishment decision after the eu commission notified the member governments on july 18th of the talks with the us government .
