on 7th this month , the us government announced the exemption of high tariff on 61 types of imported steel products and said a list of more products free from high tariff is under way .
analysts here pointed out that eu &apos;s notification of retaliatory trade measures to wto is a further step of bringing pressure to the us government , forcing us to make more concessions in the eu-us steel trade dispute .
u.s. adventurer flies off on an around-the-world hot-air balloon journey
