helanshan mountain becomes a treasure bank of animals and plants genes in northwest china
yinchuan , june25 , xinhua ( jiang xuecheng , li yunlu ) with the continuous improvement of the ecological environment , helanshan mountain , a state nature reserve , has become a veritable &quot; treasure bank of animals and plants in northwest china &quot; .
