helanshan mountain , extending more than 250 kilometers to the north and south , is situated in the border area of ningxia and inner mongolia , two large autonomous regions . it is an important natural and geographical border , a water resource conservation forest and a natural ecological defense for the attacks of tenggeli desert and siberia cold wave .
once for a while the ecological environment in the mountain area was severely destroyed due to the overgrazing and willful felling of forest . the resources of animals and plants reduced sharply .
since 1988 , china has assigned nearly 2.3 million mu lands inside ningxia as a nature reserve under state protection . in 1995 china and germany began to carry out the project &quot; ecological shelter forest at the east foot of helanshan mountain &quot; .
this year the work of closing the whole mountain to livestock grazing is officially listed as natural forest protection project of china &apos;s western region development .
after the great efforts of closing mountain to facilitate afforestation , artificial afforestation and forbidding grazing , the ecological environment here has improved apparently and all species of wild animals and plants resources have been effectively protected .
at present the forest covering rate in the helanshan mountain area has increased to 14 % from less than 10 % in the past , 690 species of wild plants live and multiply in the reserve , inner mongolian almond tree , sihe tree and sand ilex have increased abundantly , according to the sources of the administrative department of the reserve .
now there are as many as 170 species of wild animals in the nature reserve of helanshan mountain , the number of burhel merely has surpassed 10,000 .
