france : number of unemployed increases once again
paris , june 28 , ( xinhua ) french ministry of labor announced on june 28 the number of unemployed in france increased 0.5 % in may this year after the decrease in april , the number reached 2.2325 million by the end of the month .
and according to the calculating standard of the bureau of international labor , the unemployment rate in may in france still remained 9.1 % as last month .
since this year , with the amelioration of the economic condition , signs of improvement of the employment in france also appear , but there are still ups and downs .
on january the number of unemployed in france decreased the first time after the continuous 8 months of increase , the number rose again in february and march decreased once more in april .
the national institute of statistics and economic studies of france once predicted by the end of june the unemployment rate in france would reach 9.2 % .
it is presumed in the economic situation report issued by the institute on june 27 that the employment situation in france in the later part of this year will be heading toward stability . the new employment opportunities will be 950,000 the whole year and the unemployment rate will remain about 9.1 % by the end of this year .
panama : economy keeps declining
panama city , june 28 , ( xinhua ) according to the reports on june 28 , the budget committee of panama legislative parliament announced a report the other day saying that all kinds of statistics show there is no sign of improvement of the economy in panama , but continue to head for &quot; recession &quot; .
the report pointed out the panama government had not taken effective measures for solving the serious problem of financial deficit and stimulating the economy out of recession .
the report showed that the financial revenue of panama sharply reduced due to the economic decline .
according to the plan 1.19 billion us dollars should be levied in the first quarter of this year , but only 880,000,000 us dollars were actually collected , with the insufficiency as much as 310,000,000 us dollars .
although the panama government has decided to cut 150,000,000 us dollars of public expenditure this year , this will affect the investment in social and welfare services .
the report made by the budget committee of legislative parliament said that the cause of the economic slump of panama included the government corruption and lack of effective economic development plan . meanwhile the investment plan has not been carried out .
since the panama government took office in 1999 , the economic growth rate decreased year by year . the economic growth rates from 1998 to 2001 are 4.2 % , 3.2 % , 2.7 % and 0.3 % .
the panama government predicted the economic growth rate this year would be 1 % to 1.5 % . but according to a latest estimate of a panama private evaluation firm , negative growth will appear in the economy and the unemployment rate will be increased to some extent .
a hamas bomb expert assassinated by israeli troops in nablus
gaza , june 30 , xinhua ( wang hao ) a special israeli army unit assassinated on the night of june 30 a bomb expert of the islamic movement ( hamas ) in the west bank town of nablus , palestinian security sources said .
the sources said that the hamas member killed was named taher . the special israeli army unit headed nearby the apartment of taher amid the night .
at that time taher was gathering outside his home with several palestinians .
the israeli soldiers shot these people all of a sudden and killed taher and another hamas member , with another one severely injured who was sent to a nearby hospital now for emergent treatment .
israeli radio quoted an israeli army source as saying that taher was topping the most wanted list of israeli military information department . he was accused of plotting a number of suicides bombing attacks against israeli civilians .
